description:

title: Downloadable Crepe Paper Poinsettia Template/PDF Printable Download/DIY Paper Flower Template/Paper Poinsettia Template/Flower Tutorial
description:
Make your own crepe paper poinsettias using this downloadable digital template. The template allows you to make poinsettias ranging in size from about 5" in diameter up to about 10" in diameter.

The download includes:
- Printable PDF template for regular 8.5" by 11" printer paper
- Written step-by-step instructions

Photos showing each step can also be found on my website www.citrinepaperflowers.com (and while you're there, sign up for my e-newsletter to get special freebies!)

You will need to provide your own supplies. Supplies you will need for making 1 poinsettia:
- Printer paper or cardstock to print out template
- Scissors
- Tacky craft glue
- Crepe paper of any thickness (about 4" by 20" area of crepe paper up to 8" by 20" area for the petals depending on the size, and about 4" by 20" area of green crepe paper)
- Thin floral wire (about 26 gauge, 4'-5' length)
- Floral stem wire or barbeque skewer for the stem

Benefits:
- Save money by making your own flower arrangement and holiday decor!
- You can re-use the template to make as many flowers as you want
- Handmade flowers are unique and they don't wilt so you can cherish them forever

Notes:
- This template is meant to be used with crepe paper, and not cardstock or other types of paper that don't stretch.
- Template is for personal use only (no commercial use or sharing!)

title: Crepe Paper Roses DIY Kit
description:
Create your very own beautiful roses that will last and last with my handcrafted DIY Crepe Paper Roses Kit.

This kit contains high quality floristry crepe paper, floristry wires, templates, a curling stick and full colour easy to follow instructions. All you need are scissors and PVA/craft glue.

This kit comes in a variety of colours and makes 3 beautiful flowers.

This kit is plastic free (including the packaging) and all printing is done on an ecotank printer.

I offer full support, via email, social media or telephone, with all kit purchases.

First class delivery is included in the price of this craft kit and the kit fits through a regular letterbox.

Suitable for beginners and children over 12 Years.

With this kit you will learn how to cut, mold and shape the leaves, petals and other components of the rose before assembling your beautiful creation.

Please note that the crepe paper in these kits is 180 gsm, it is not the thin crepe paper used for streamers. This crepe paper is very thick and mouldable and, in most cases, is bleed proof and fade proof.

Please note, colours may vary slightly to those shown, dependant on your monitors settings.
